  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Text Adventure Game - Halloween Edition!</h1>
        <h2>An exciting game of Trick or Treating and Suspense!</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="text">
        SYSTEM INITIALIZATION COMPLETE<br>
        HALLOWEEN ADVENTURE SYSTEM V2.1<br>
        COPYRIGHT (C) 1982 MYSTERY SOFTWARE CORP.<br><br>
        > LOADING ENVIRONMENT DATA...<br>
