        > WEATHER: COLD AND WINDY<br>
        > TIME: 6:30 PM, OCTOBER 31ST<br><br>
        You are standing on Elm Street. The autumn wind rustles<br>
        through bare tree branches overhead. Jack-o'-lanterns<br>
